  "title": "Homecare Community Staff Nurse (office hours) #HJO",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Assess and take comprehensive history of patients under her charge.</li><li>Develop and implement plan of care.</li><li>Perform follow-up review of patients under his/her charge; coordinate and evaluate care using appropriate care plans.</li><li>Perform procedures which are within the scope of duties.</li><li>Patient education</li><li>Provide specialised patient education / caregiver training.</li><li>Implement and coordinate individualised and group learning programmes with patients/caregivers.</li><li>Evaluate effectiveness of patient education; perform health education and discharge teaching to patients/families/caregivers</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Min. Diploma / Degree in Nursing</li><li>Min 3 to 4 years of ward / Geriatric / nursing home / homecare exp</li></ul><p><br />Interested candidates are invited to email your resume to:</p><p>jen.ooi@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>Jenalyn Ooi Huai Sian (R1765551)</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd  | Company Reg. No. 199601303W | EA License Number: 99C4599</p><p></p><p></p>",
